'''奧莉維亞·伊莎貝爾·羅德里戈'''（{{Lang-en|Olivia Isabel Rodrigo}}，{{Bd|2003年|2月20日}}），是一名美國創作歌手及演員。<ref>{{Cite web|title=Olivia Rodrigo reassesses the meaning of forever on stunning piano-led debut “drivers license”|url=https://www.thelineofbestfit.com/new-music/song-of-the-day/olivia-rodrigo-drivers-license|accessdate=2021-01-16|work=The Line of Best Fit|language=en|archive-date=2021-01-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210109010245/https://www.thelineofbestfit.com/new-music/song-of-the-day/olivia-rodrigo-drivers-license|dead-url=no}}</ref>她因在[[迪士尼頻道|迪士尼頻道]][[剧集|系列影集]]《{{Link-en|Bizaardvark|Bizaardvark}}》中扮演Paige Olvera而聞名，並在[[Disney+|Disney+]]系列影集《[[歌舞青春：再谱乐曲系列|歌舞青春：再谱乐曲系列]]》中扮演Nini Salazar-Roberts。她於2021年1月發行了首張單曲〈[[駕照_(奧莉維亞·羅德里戈歌曲)|駕照]]〉，也在同年5月發行了首張專輯《[[SOUR|SOUR]]》。<ref>{{Cite web|title=Olivia Rodrigo's Debut Single 'Drivers License' Has Already Made Streaming History|url=https://musicfeeds.com.au/news/olivia-rodrigos-debut-single-drivers-license-has-already-made-streaming-history/|accessdate=2021-01-16|date=2021-01-13|work=Music Feeds|archive-date=2021-01-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210115014331/https://musicfeeds.com.au/news/olivia-rodrigos-debut-single-drivers-license-has-already-made-streaming-history/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=Olivia Rodrigo’s ‘Drivers License’ Hits No. 1 Across Major Streaming Platforms, Earns Praise From Taylor Swift|url=https://variety.com/2021/music/news/olivia-rodrigo-drivers-license-spotify-apple-music-amazon-taylor-swift-1234882800/|accessdate=2021-01-16|date=2021-01-11|last=Shafer|first=Ellise|work=Variety|language=en-US|archive-date=2021-01-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210112121513/https://variety.com/2021/music/news/olivia-rodrigo-drivers-license-spotify-apple-music-amazon-taylor-swift-1234882800/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

